"""
        choose values that simplify the calculations and are similar to
        observed values
    """
w = firm.get_w(Y, L, p, method)
assert np.allclose(w, expected, atol=1e-06)

    expected1), (Y1, L1, p2, 'SS', expected2), (Y1, L1, p3, 'SS', expected3
    ), (Y4, L4, p4, 'TPI', expected4)], ids=['epsilon=0.2,SS',
    'epsilon=1.5,SS', 'epsilon=1.0,SS', 'epsilon=1.2,TP'])
